{"tid":498691,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"一人一個細個做過嘅柒事 一世都有陰影","createTime":"2017-12-14T05:06:27.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-14T14:13:01.000Z","uid":139826,"like":20,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"af3db6681dde18851e3f6220d60ba8d9b5749f01","tid":498691,"uid":139826,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-14T05:06:27.000Z","msg":"⚠️我先⚠️<br />\n<br />\n細個對性好奇 襯屋企冇人 <br />\n用電腦上埋啲不知明嘅咸網<br />\n點撚知中咗毒 啲咸網係咁彈上黎 關唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n屋企人返到之後用電腦 見到咸網係咁彈係咁彈<br />\n就估到我上完咸網中毒  比老母拎藤條屌打我<br />\n諗起都真係柒到仆街<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c3a39b08fc212a2111dd3d44681a536fb1513e21","tid":498691,"uid":139826,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-14T05:07:31.000Z","msg":"Pish"},{"pid":"2c22798c76f9f38a1a58ab476aa7401a9455a154","tid":498691,"uid":139826,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-14T05:10:04.000Z","msg":"Pish"},{"pid":"531836e0cf2f87dd988e318963f0ea2d7be5a775","tid":498691,"uid":21006,"like":34,"dislike":2,"score":32,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-14T05:18:24.000Z","msg":"以前中學同小學生補習，我係負責幫手教，咁有個小學生唔識膝頭點讀，咁果陣我唔肯定係讀'室'頭定'柒'頭，咁我教佢讀'柒'頭。<br />\n點知個補習老師叫個小學生讀成篇野比佢聽，跟住小學生緊係讀啦，讀到去膝頭果陣，佢記得我教佢讀柒頭，佢就讀左出黎。<br />\n之後補習班老師問佢「柒頭？你就柒頭」，之後瘋狂咁屌個小學生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"712a34167333efd97bdc093161f89303b3e2bb85","tid":498691,"uid":139826,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-14T05:27:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>以前中學同小學生補習，我係負責幫手教，咁有個小學生唔識膝頭點讀，咁果陣我唔肯定係讀'室'頭定'柒'頭，咁我教佢讀'柒'頭。<br />\n點知個補習老師叫個小學生讀成篇野比佢聽，跟住小學生緊係讀啦，讀到去膝頭果陣，佢記得我教佢讀柒頭，佢就讀左出黎。<br />\n之後補習班老師問佢「柒頭？你就柒頭」，之後瘋狂咁屌個小學生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n呢個好笑呀柒頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3de245e5d489d83f2174ee8a1c1751601bb89777","tid":498691,"uid":146726,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-14T05:29:02.000Z","msg":"係街叫錯第二個女人做媽咪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n仲要拖住佢隻手叫佢 點知認撚錯左老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d1c78c3fb61d8fa51cfdb57c4c6cf4b1610df69","tid":498691,"uid":21006,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-14T05:29:23.000Z","msg":"睇住個小學生比補習老師屌都好好笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"35c65303851187e6f2c55a1e9c71dcf4e4307b66","tid":498691,"uid":135197,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-14T05:30:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>係街叫錯第二個女人做媽咪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n仲要拖住佢隻手叫佢 點知認撚錯左老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n試過追住第二個女人嗌媽咪<br />\n跟住真老母係後面叫住我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bafa79f418a8496ad4402190ace48062306d59d2","tid":498691,"uid":21006,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-14T05:30:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>睇住個小學生比補習老師屌都好好笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n自此之後，我就識讀膝頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c8bdddcffc8bb4b8b36f025b76db3baee058059","tid":498691,"uid":61545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-14T06:24:30.000Z","msg":"小學英文作文想寫筆盒嘅英文<br />\n唔識串pencilcase寫咗做pencilcave<br />\n個英文老師用咗20分鐘係全班面前一路鬧一路恥笑我<br />\n怒羞成怒嘅我當場撕爛咗份作文然後走咗成堂英文<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a11bda10eae570c8f8a67b3280c096a61e0ea8e2","tid":498691,"uid":117417,"like":8,